title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 9/1 -  Mike Grimm, New WR in Town, 10 Reasons
description: Gophers football radio VOX Mike Grimm stops by to preview Gophers/New Mexico State, the rest of the Big 10 week 1 slate, & more.  PA & Nordo break down the Vikings trade for WR Jalen Reagor, and give you 10 reasons why the Vikings will beat the Packers 10 days from now.
